task.summary: Minor update Implemented new parameters in PendingRegisterLocation Cleaned bits of code.
Version 1.5.2 finished Implemented restriction in HandsetLocation

Implemented bug report system (2/2) Now sends the report when the app comes back up
Fixed bug in UpdateStatusActivity, updated to 1.5.4 Caused by not selecting a checkbox.
Fixed crashing in LoginActivity Surrounded spinners with try-catch blocks.
Updated to version 1.5.5 Fixed crash while logging in.
Fixed a crash due to NullPointerException, added try-catch.
Fixed another crash due to NullPointerException, added try-catch.
Fixed a crash of WindowManager.BadTokenException. Surrounded with try-catch
Toast of a problem with db
Changed an AdviceUser code to prevent a crash.
